title: Classy Zilkerian Townhouse w/2-Car Garage, Rooftop Terrace, WALKABLITY
posting_body: Hey check out this spacious 3-level townhouse in the red hot ZILKER neighborhood with excellent walk ability.
Direct access to the Lamar Union Square development via private gate.
Take a $5 fasten to your favorite west six street bars and restaurants or go for a relaxing jog around town lake.

This townhouse has a open floor plan, huge master bedroom with double closets, Jacuzzi tub, office/extra bedroom on first floor, roof top terrace with downtown views, granite countertops, and last but not least Google fiber!
